jasima.shopSim.util

类 TextFileReader

  • java.lang.Object
    • jasima.shopSim.util.TextFileReader

  • public class TextFileReader
extends java.lang.Object
    This class creates a ShopDef based on the contents of a text file. This can be used to configure a Shop, e.g., as part of a StaticShopExperiment. For examples of the file structure see the examples in the directory "testInstances" or the model files in the package jasima.shopSim.models.mimac.
    作者:
    Torsten Hildebrandt
